    "en_q": "A developer is building an ecommerce application that uses multiple AWS Lambda functions. Each function performs a specific step in a customer order workflow, such as order processing and inventory management. The developer must ensure that the Lambda functions run in a specific order. Which solution will meet this requirement with the LEAST operational overhead?",
